{"tid":2070650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"姐係chickeeduck個周小龍背後金主係深紅人大?","createTime":"2020-06-19T09:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T08:00:19.000Z","uid":3055,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5b5dc59abe174057982e15998219baf8f222dc71","tid":2070650,"uid":3055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:16:36.000Z","msg":"01唔貼LINK，初選<br />\n<br />\n----------------------<br />\n撰文：周偉強陳潤南李穎霖<br />\n2020-06-19 16:44<br />\n最後更新日期：2020-06-19 17:03<br />\n連鎖童裝店Chickeeduck行政總裁周小龍日前於荃灣愉景新城分店，擺放持「光復香港」旗幟的「民主女神像」，惟商場管理方要求移走雕像。<br />\n<br />\n《香港01》發現，2019年「Chickeeduck」的公司申報，行政總裁周小龍只持股4成，另外6成股份為親建制胡法光家族持有，公司董事之一胡曉明為現任全國人大、中華總商會副會長。然而，於「Chickeeduck」擺放女神像後，中華總商會的胡曉明介紹，將原本的「Chickeeduck」董事職位刪走。<br />\n<br />\n周小龍發言人未有正面回應公司變動。胡曉明發言人回覆，胡氏家族已在6月12日出讓全部Chickeeduck 股權並辭任董事；周小龍先生支持反修例運動屬其個人行為，胡曉明、胡亮明和集團完全不認同。<br />\n<br />\n連鎖童裝店Chickeeduck日前於荃灣愉景新城分店，擺放持「光復香港」旗幟的「民主女神像」，行政總裁周小龍亦表明支持反修例運動。（資料圖片／羅國輝攝）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據「Chickeeduck Retail (Hong Kong) Limited」（下文簡稱「Chickeeduck」） 2019年的周年申報表，除周小龍外，「電梯大王」胡法光之子胡曉明亦是公司董事。胡曉明現為「菱電發展」主席，第13 屆全國人大代表，及現任中華總商會副會長。胡胞弟「菱電發展」副主席胡亮明於2019年同為「Chickeeduck」董事。公司另一董事陳思銚同時亦於多間與胡氏家族有關的「菱電集團」公司，任職董事。<br />\n<br />\n據Chickeeduck去年的周年申報表，「電梯大王」胡法光之子、全國人大代表胡曉明為公司股東之一。（資料圖片／梁鵬威攝）<br />\n<br />\n胡亮明11日仍任公司主席 胡曉明網頁刪董事職銜<br />\n<br />\n公司註冊處資料顯示，胡亮明於11日仍以「Chickeeduck」主席身份主持會議，會議地點為「菱電發展」辦公室。「Chickeeduck」於18日再向公司註冊處遞交「更改秘書或董事通知」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，周小龍於16日於荃灣愉景新城分店擺放「民主女神像」。事件後，胡曉明於中華總商會網頁，簡歷中刪去了「 Chickeeduck Retail (Hong Kong) Limited」董事職銜，刪除時間為本月17日早上之後。另外，胡曉明的個人網頁近日亦刪去了「 Chickeeduck Retail (Hong Kong) Limited」董事職銜，根據資料，6月4日前仍可見到上述資料，但未知實際刪除日期。胡今個月初曾於《文匯報》發表文章，指國安法可以完善一國兩制。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200619/350672300959469568.jpeg/VK-XreCZ_D2GpX1iJDnbBlUhvoV-5rsI2Lej2di3o9k?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200619%2F350672300959469568.jpeg%2FVK-XreCZ_D2GpX1iJDnbBlUhvoV-5rsI2Lej2di3o9k%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=5b6ab72b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港中華總商會網頁上，介紹胡曉明的頁面已刪去Chickeeduck Retail (Hong Kong) Limited董事職銜。（中華總商會網頁截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200619/350677623388639232.jpeg/Bxk-4vLLCphyQJBxa2DbrJup1sLMBPhqVzFZ4lcxWeI?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200619%2F350677623388639232.jpeg%2FBxk-4vLLCphyQJBxa2DbrJup1sLMBPhqVzFZ4lcxWeI%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=c95c6451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n胡曉明個人網站的簡歷亦已將Chickeeduck Retail (Hong Kong) Limited董事職銜刪去。（胡曉明個人網站截圖）<br />\n<br />\n「Chickeeduck」原大股東為胡氏家族<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200619/350682994748559360.jpeg/hXRog9drWLFLvJb1CH8ACLAxGsHo60bFQvlXGkL5Vxo?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200619%2F350682994748559360.jpeg%2FhXRog9drWLFLvJb1CH8ACLAxGsHo60bFQvlXGkL5Vxo%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=1e06afcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據2019年周年申報表，「Chickeeduck」的股份，絕大部份由「潤信貿易有限公司」擁有。同年周小龍持「潤信貿易」四成股份，胡曉明、胡亮明兄弟分別持一成，另外四成則為胡法光及其妻有份持有的「尚紀設計有限公司」擁有。換言之，胡法光家族同年共持有「Chickeeduck」 六成股份。<br />\n<br />\n去年持Chickeeduck絕大部分的潤發貿易有限公司，周小龍只持股4成，其餘6成股份為胡法光家族成員，及其旗下公司持有。（公司註冊處）<br />\n<br />\n胡曉明：完全不認同周小龍<br />\n<br />\n記者向周小龍查詢公司最近變動及與原股東有沒有因事件不和，周的發言人表示，問題與今次活動無關，又說「有關你所問嘅問題，相信你可以自己查到。」<br />\n<br />\n另外胡曉明發言人回覆《香港01》，胡氏家族已在6月12日出讓全部「Chickeeduck」股權並辭任；周小龍先生支持反修例運動屬其個人行為，胡曉明、胡亮明先生和集團完全不認同。集團一直支持香港特區政府依法施政，保持香港繁榮安定。<br />\n<br />\n胡曉明發言人回覆《香港01》指，家族已在6月12日出讓全部Chickeeduck 股權並辭任，又稱完全不認同周小龍支持反修例運動的行為。（資料圖片／蔡正邦攝）<br />\n<br />\n胡法光是菱電集團的創辦人，有「電梯大王」之稱，於2016年獲頒大紫荊勳章，同年獲頒大紫荊包括特首林鄭月娥及香港大學前校長徐立之等。「菱電發展」目前主要業務為地產開發及物業管理等，包括早年與影星周星馳合作發展山頂超級豪宅「天比高」。<br />\n<br />\n有「電梯大王」之稱的胡法光（右），於2016年10月獲時任行政長官梁振英頒授大紫荆勛章。（新華社）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港城市大學於2010年，將校內運動中心冠胡法光（中）之名，其子胡曉明亦曾為城大校董會主席。（香港城市大學網頁截圖）"},{"pid":"387169a76a91a921264610adf98a4d038ddc400e","tid":2070650,"uid":3055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:17:35.000Z","msg":"初選淺黃會否中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be6582914aba94bb910157a9ee3882083d97247c","tid":2070650,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:19:48.000Z","msg":"都係嗰句<br />\n聯署+初選先投"},{"pid":"a7fd24fbe8789499c2684650fbe8cbe30148109b","tid":2070650,"uid":7179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:21:59.000Z","msg":"香港人又又又又又再一次中計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"970d457b4d439aa79a0e7501f961d8fd61fda059","tid":2070650,"uid":343153,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:25:41.000Z","msg":"盲既都睇到咩事啦，仲話自已一年前己經去69遊行，但繼續同紅底partner合作成年........ 仲要前幾日先退股，過兩日走出黎話選，仲要唔肯初選攬抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下次扮黃都扮好啲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ff6cbc632d5f8b74e97e3f5976d5bee2f0e860","tid":2070650,"uid":271398,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:31:15.000Z","msg":"條友扮黃扮到出哂面<br />\n放個像就俾班黃絲捧上神枱<br />\n香港人真係好好呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb09f708cc588d01ff51916a242a222c40fa5f77","tid":2070650,"uid":160147,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:32:22.000Z","msg":"咁支那仲制唔制裁間舖好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？？？"},{"pid":"537f947738731ffd3f5364070a3402045e27c081","tid":2070650,"uid":54800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:55:04.000Z","msg":"18/6《星期三港案》港商「童」行<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TXqYZrmP1kc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTXqYZrmP1kc&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84CwAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=65829519\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TXqYZrmP1kc</a><br />\n<br />\n就算係背景紅底.....<br />\n佢D客係藍一樣會因為佢放左個民主女神像...而少左去果間店買野....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76142ba3601fc4f05648ea1d214f2ff5049b4a1f","tid":2070650,"uid":61806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed522f0f473e5b54f87e6382e50b992a5c12042","tid":2070650,"uid":53321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:08:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"082623caa945fa206110ba79248077910fbf2742","tid":2070650,"uid":53321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:08:26.000Z","msg":"平時鋪頭都算 但條友仲話要出黎選"},{"pid":"7f1f0e59769ce0fa7528e08d76a0ae92daa9edeb","tid":2070650,"uid":53321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:09:15.000Z","msg":"推上去比人見到"},{"pid":"78d7289e90f81c859bc85678d403906129c77108","tid":2070650,"uid":53321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:09:55.000Z","msg":"選舉唔鬥黃幾時鬥？"},{"pid":"9263a1260da17a12c052c78964d1e15cfea23f42","tid":2070650,"uid":69797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T10:35:00.000Z","msg":"佢有篇訪問 係講上年反修例先覺醒<br />\n而家佢肯企前 胡氏劃清界線<br />\n點都要撐左先 撐到大家都知扮黃係香港先有出路<br />\n咁先可以掩護真黃"},{"pid":"85979b1365e6d860c8b2fa52d620ef85417c96a4","tid":2070650,"uid":358254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T11:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"9511269d7985a2cbe8ff9f117cdfaee9f8a14a63","tid":2070650,"uid":255274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T11:34:26.000Z","msg":"過左成年 又會而家先突然咁黃"},{"pid":"1bde5dc0b42732599962c4654e2f1fc0878384af","tid":2070650,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T11:37:41.000Z","msg":"真係相當有嫌疑<br />\n首先無啦啦有人爆咗個人像，之後無啦啦又話參選<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2739b19f47f14c3d54879d06764bc683050a8d88","tid":2070650,"uid":346240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T11:47:38.000Z","msg":"扮黃仆街過藍"},{"pid":"cfb946a7d715cdd69489a2f4b9ea20da3898f712","tid":2070650,"uid":237838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T08:00:19.000Z","msg":"之前有報導話胡生已經事後辭職<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}